<h3>Summon Elemental Blanket</h3>
<p>This is one of the best summoned resistance items magicians get.&nbsp; The
Elemental Blanket is a +15 save fire, save cold and save magic item wearable in
the shoulders or back slot by all classes.&nbsp; It is LORE, so only one may be
worn.&nbsp; Your pet likely will equip two of these since mobs can clearly drop
duplicate LORE items.&nbsp; I've not seen an official Verant statement on this
point.</p>

